          transliteration: "kānyakubjē dvijavarḥ sa hyajāmila ityabhūt\nvēdavitsuvratayutaḥ sadācāraparō'malaḥ |\npitrōḥ śuśrūṣaṇaratō guruvṛttiparāyaṇaḥ\nśraddadhānō jitēndriyaḥ saṁyatō niyatēndriyaḥ ||",
